<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Retro Movie Merchandise</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Permanent+Marker&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap');

        body {
            background-color: #112C33;
            color: #F0EADE;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #4F1025;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: 'Permanent Marker', cursive;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #FCCC13;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem; 
            transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            color: #f4c273;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .hero {
            background: url('IMAGE_URL_HERE') no-repeat center center/cover; /* Replace IMAGE_URL_HERE */
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Permanent Marker', cursive;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #E1DA55;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px #4E5021;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-family: 'Permanent Marker', cursive;
            color: #f4c273;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #4E5021;
            color: #E6DBCE;
            border: 1px solid #F1EFE2;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #F1EFE2;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #E1DA55;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #4F1025;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #F0EADE;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/products">Products</a>
        <a href="/favorites">Favorites</a>
        <a href="/basket">Basket</a>
        <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/users/profile">Profile</a>
            <a href="/users/logout">Logout</a>
            <% if (user.username === 'admin') { %>
                <a href="/admin">Admin</a>
                <a href="/users">Users</a>
            <% } %>
        <% } else { %>
            <a href="/users/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/users/register">Register</a>
        <% } %>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to Retro Movie Merchandise</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Featured Products</h2>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/nightjarprod/content/uploads/sites/4/2018/07/09170404/breakfastclub_poster.jpg" alt="...">
                <h3>The Breakfast Club</h3>
                <p>Everyone is different.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Back_to_the_Future.jpg" alt="...">
                <h3>Back to the Future</h3>
                <p>If we can identify our mistakes and our limitations, we can correct them and improve ourselves.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.moviesanywhere.com/34f4f25b50973b8fe2b197c8a8a6e3a5/1a9ea9c0-fb38-439b-977e-40b6fe52a006.jpg" alt="...">
                <h3>E.T.</h3>
                <p>Accepting others who are different.</p>
            </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>We specialize in selling iconic merchandise from the most beloved movies of the 80s and 90s. From classic action figures to rare collector's items, we have it all!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Retro Movie Merchandise. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Contact Us: info@retromoviemerchandise.com</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
